title: Logo Font
content:
I am doing some design work for a local pool store and like TOO MANY business they don't have a hi-res or vector file of their logo. So I'm trying to recreate it and would like to use the font that was originally used to create it. But I'm stumped.

Here's the current logo: [http://www.flickr.com/photos/khedaywi/1809370610/](http://web.archive.org/web/20131020191845/http:/www.flickr.com/photos/khedaywi/1809370610/)

Any ideas on the font??

Thanks!
author: khedaywi

comments.content:
